Velocity Selector Simulator
===========================

Short compilation instructions:
--------------------------------

At the src folder (if not there, cd ./src)

For compiling with IntelÂ® Fortran (if already installed) run:

./build.sh ifort

For compiling with GNU-Fortran (if already installed), run:

./build.sh gfortran

If the compilation ends successfully, a executable file named "wien_filter" will appear at the src directory.